T02TD2068E:156b-1: shr'i dzi ya sunda ri s'a dha nam /
T02TD2068E:156b-3: dpal rgyal ba'i mdzes ma'i sgrub thabs /
T02TD2068E:156b-4: aom shr'i dzi ya sunda ri h'um /
T02TD2068E:156b-6: chu klung gnyis phrad pa'i sar tsandan gyi mandala byas te /
T02TD2068E:156b-7: mchod pa dang gtor ma dang zan dang zho phul nas /
T02TD2068E:156b-8: zhag bdun du nyi ma re la stong phrag brgyad brgyad bzlas pas /
T02TD2068E:156b-9: zhag bdun gyi nub mo rgyan dang bcas nges par 'ong ngo //
T02TD2068E:156b-10: byung ba dang chu'i mchod yon dbul lo //
T02TD2068E:156b-11: de dgyes nas bu bdag gis ci bgyi zhes zer na bdag nyid rgyal por gyis shig ces brjod do //
T02TD2068E:156b-12: des rgyal po dang gos dang rgyan dang zas la sogs pa rnams ster bar 'gyur ro //
T02TD2068E:156b-13: dpal rgyal ba'i mdzes ma zhes bya ba'i sgrub thabs rdzogs so//
